author: Inside Edition
description: It's the Swedish take on an American icon. The Philly cheesesteak is a delicious combination of beef, cheese and other toppings you might prefer. Now a food truck in the Nordic country is serving it up with a different kind of meat, reindeer. Inside Edition Digital’s Mara Montalbano has more.
title: Food Truck in Sweden Serves $26 Cheesesteak Sandwich with Reindeer Meat

author: Inside Edition
description: Would you wear this uncommon clothing? In 2019, a colorful, flowy garment had people asking, is this a nightgown or a dress? In 2022, plastic from Covid-19 vaccine syringes was turned into interesting attire. In 2023, fashion blogger Anita Mwiruki took to social media to express her surprise after receiving a dress that looked a little different than what she expected. Inside Edition Digital's Andrea Swindall has more.
title: Would You Wear This Uncommon Clothing
